<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>TabibAI | AI Clinic Assistant</title>
  <meta name="description" content="AI-powered WhatsApp assistant for clinics in Saudi Arabia. Book appointments, reduce no-shows, and increase clinic revenue." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #07111f;
      --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --card-2: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      --text: #f4f8fb;
      --muted: #b5c3d1;
      --primary: #10c7b2;
      --primary-dark: #0fa391;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      --radius: 22px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(16,199,178,0.15), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 0% 20%, rgba(16,199,178,0.12), transparent 25%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #07111f 0%, #0b1930 100%);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .navbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      background: rgba(7, 17, 31, 0.7);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .nav-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 16px 0;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .brand-badge {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #7af1e2);
      color: #04221e;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 22px;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #4be8d3);
      color: #03221e;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(16,199,178,0.25);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-color: var(--line);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 72px 0 42px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 34px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(16,199,178,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(16,199,178,0.25);
      color: #93fff1;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.6rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .lead {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.14rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      min-width: 150px;
    }

    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .mockup {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .phone {
      border-radius: 28px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: #0f172a;
      max-width: 410px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .phone-top {
      background: #0b1930;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .chat {
      padding: 18px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eff6ff, #f8fafc);
    }

    .bubble {
      max-width: 78%;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15,23,42,0.05);
    }

    .bubble.bot {
      background: white;
      border-top-left-radius: 6px;
      justify-self: start;
    }

    .bubble.user {
      background: #d1fae5;
      border-top-right-radius: 6px;
      justify-self: end;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 56px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }

    .section-lead {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 720px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .grid-4 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.16rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .card p, .card li {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .steps {
      counter-reset: step;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .step {
      position: relative;
      padding-top: 54px;
    }

    .step::before {
      counter-increment: step;
      content: counter(step);
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #72efe0);
      color: #06221f;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .pricing {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .price-box {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      margin: 10px 0 4px;
    }

    .price small {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .checklist {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .checklist li::before {
      content: "✓";
      color: #8ff8eb;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    .cta-box {
      padding: 36px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16,199,178,0.16), rgba(255,255,255,0.06));
      border: 1px solid rgba(16,199,178,0.26);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 36px 0 60px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .footer-wrap {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding-top: 22px;
    }

    .contact-form {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font: inherit;
      outline: none;
    }

    .contact-form textarea {
      min-height: 120px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .muted { color: var(--muted); }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-grid, .pricing, .grid-4, .steps {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero { padding-top: 42px; }
      .section { padding: 42px 0; }
      .cta-box { padding: 26px; }
      .card { padding: 20px; }
      .brand span:last-child { font-size: 1rem; }
      .container { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 20px)); }
    }
  </style>
  <script defer src="https://cdn.vercel-insights.com/v1/script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container nav-wrap">
      <a class="brand" href="#top">
        <div class="brand-badge">T</div>
        <span>TabibAI</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#how">How it works</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Start Free Trial</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">AI WhatsApp assistant for clinics in Saudi Arabia</div>
          <h1>Turn missed appointments into revenue.</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            TabibAI automates patient booking, reminders, and clinic communication on WhatsApp — helping clinics reduce no-shows, save staff time, and grow revenue.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Start Free Trial</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#how">See How It Works</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>24/7</strong>
              <span class="muted">patient replies</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>30%</strong>
              <span class="muted">fewer no-shows target</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>399 SAR</strong>
              <span class="muted">monthly starter plan</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="phone">
            <div class="phone-top">
              <span>TabibAI Assistant</span>
              <span>WhatsApp</span>
            </div>
            <div class="chat">
              <div class="bubble bot">Welcome to Al Noor Dental Clinic 👋 How can I help you today?<br>1. Book appointment<br>2. Clinic location<br>3. Services</div>
              <div class="bubble user">Book appointment</div>
              <div class="bubble bot">Please choose a service:<br>• Cleaning<br>• Filling<br>• Consultation</div>
              <div class="bubble user">Cleaning tomorrow</div>
              <div class="bubble bot">Available times:<br>10:00 AM<br>12:00 PM<br>4:00 PM</div>
              <div class="bubble user">10 AM</div>
              <div class="bubble bot">✅ Your appointment is confirmed for tomorrow at 10:00 AM.<br>We’ll send you a reminder before your visit.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Built for how clinics actually work</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">Most clinics already use WhatsApp every day. TabibAI turns that behavior into a simple revenue system instead of more admin work.</p>
        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Missed appointments cost money</h3>
            <p>Unconfirmed bookings and forgotten visits leave gaps in the schedule and directly reduce clinic revenue.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Reception is overloaded</h3>
            <p>Staff spend too much time answering repeat questions, checking times, and chasing patients manually.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Patients expect fast replies</h3>
            <p>When clinics answer late, patients often book elsewhere. Speed matters more than most clinics realize.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Everything your clinic needs to automate bookings</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">Start simple with the highest-ROI features first, then expand into voice AI, analytics, and advanced workflows.</p>
        <div class="grid-4">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>AI WhatsApp Receptionist</h3>
            <p>Replies instantly to patients, answers common questions, and starts the booking flow automatically.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Smart Scheduling</h3>
            <p>Shows available times, confirms appointments, and keeps a clean booking record for the clinic.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Automated Reminders</h3>
            <p>Reduce no-shows with scheduled reminders before appointments and follow-up messages after visits.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Clinic Dashboard</h3>
            <p>Track appointments, leads, reminder performance, and basic operational metrics in one place.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="how">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">How it works</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">This is designed to be simple for clinic teams and frictionless for patients.</p>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="card step">
            <h3>Patient sends a message</h3>
            <p>A patient reaches your clinic on WhatsApp to ask for an appointment or service.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card step">
            <h3>TabibAI replies instantly</h3>
            <p>The assistant identifies the request, offers service options, and presents time slots.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card step">
            <h3>Appointment gets confirmed</h3>
            <p>The system stores the booking and sends a confirmation with time and clinic details.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card step">
            <h3>Reminder gets delivered</h3>
            <p>Patients receive a reminder before the visit, helping the clinic keep the schedule full.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container pricing" id="pricing">
        <div class="card price-box">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:0;">Simple pricing for fast clinic adoption</h2>
            <p class="section-lead" style="margin-bottom: 0;">Start with a focused offer that is easy to sell, easy to understand, and easy to renew.</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="checklist">
            <li>WhatsApp booking automation</li>
            <li>Appointment confirmation flow</li>
            <li>Automated reminders</li>
            <li>Basic clinic dashboard</li>
            <li>Arabic and English ready</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Starter Plan</div>
          <div class="price">399 <small>SAR / month</small></div>
          <p class="muted">Perfect for dental clinics and smaller medical practices starting with WhatsApp automation.</p>
          <div style="display:grid; gap:12px; margin-top:20px;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Start 7-Day Free Trial</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#contact">Book a Demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-box">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:0;">Built for Saudi clinics. Ready to scale across the GCC.</h2>
            <p class="section-lead" style="margin:0; max-width:700px;">Start with dental clinics, prove ROI fast, and expand into dermatology, polyclinics, and broader outpatient healthcare.</p>
          </div>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Launch Your Trial</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="contact">
      <div class="container grid-3" style="align-items:start;">
        <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 2;">
          <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:0;">Start your free trial</h2>
          <p class="section-lead">Replace the form action later with your real backend or lead collection tool. For now, this is ready for direct edit and deployment.</p>
          <form class="contact-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Thanks! Replace this form with your real backend or WhatsApp link.');">
            <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px;">
              <input type="text" placeholder="Clinic name" required>
              <input type="text" placeholder="Contact person" required>
            </div>
            <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px;">
              <input type="email" placeholder="Email address" required>
              <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone / WhatsApp" required>
            </div>
            <textarea placeholder="Tell us about your clinic"></textarea>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request Demo</button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Quick contact</h3>
          <p>Email: hello@tabibai.com</p>
          <p>WhatsApp: +966 5X XXX XXXX</p>
          <p>Based in Saudi Arabia</p>
          <p class="muted">Edit these contact details before publishing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-wrap">
      <div>© 2026 TabibAI. All rights reserved.</div>
      <div>AI clinic assistant for smarter bookings, better care, and stronger clinic revenue.</div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
